headline: CoStar: Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: The average estimate of three analysts surveyed by Zacks Investment Research was for earnings of 22 cents per share. The commercial real estate information and marketing provider posted revenue of $709.4 million in the period, also surpassing Street forecasts. Three analysts surveyed by Zacks expected $701 million.
